snippet.title: Speed Running Bitzy! Speed Running My Game.
snippet.description:
Speed running my game called Bitzy. Bitzy is a 1 bit platformer full of epic bosses. The version I just finished speed running, was the 0.4 version. Bitzy is still in development, and you can play it here: https://vjsdgames.com/Bitzy

Itch.io Game Page: https://vincentjenei.itch.io/bitzy
